OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy start, with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain in the north and
OL,7,Fwest. Brightening up for many, with
OL,8,Fspells of warm sunshine developing.
OL,9,FThough staying cloudy across the
OL,10,Fnorthwest, with further rain in
OL,11,Fplaces. Locally hot in the southeast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloud and patchy rain across
OL,14,Fparts of Scotland, Northern Ireland
OL,15,Fand northern England. Largely dry
OL,16,Felsewhere, with clear spells and
OL,17,Fperhaps the odd light showers. A mild
OL,18,Fnight for most.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
