OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FWarm spells of sunshine for
OL,6,Fmuch of England and Wales. Cloudier
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland and Scotland,
OL,8,Fwith further rain here. Staying hot
OL,9,Ftowards the southeast, generally warm
OL,10,Felsewhere.
